-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note on the remote SportScore API
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

The MIT license in LICENSE covers THIS software only (the MCP server code).

The remote SportScore API this server talks to is a separate service and is
governed by the SportScore API Terms of Use:

    https://sportscore.com/developers/terms/

On the free tier those terms require a visible "Powered by SportScore"
dofollow backlink on any page or surface that renders data returned from the
API. The MCP server defaults include a `source` attribution field and a
plain-English attribution line in every tool response to make compliance the
default behaviour — please leave it in place unless you hold a commercial /
white-label agreement that removes the attribution requirement.

Commercial / white-label use: api@sportscore.com
